values: so much has changed.  I suppose that i brought alot of it upon myself. I miss my best friend but at the same time we arent who we were. As much as i still wish we were close our interactions seem rare and akward which i hate. I really just dont know what to do or think about that. I know that you feel i betrayed you and that its something you arent going to be able to forget. Im sorry. Just remember that i would never do anything to deliberatley hurt you. I really thought i was helping, I was worried. Ive realized that you will do what you want though and I plan to stay out of it unless you voice a wanting of me to do otherwise. All of this has showed me a different side of you and I wonder how much the three of us actually knew eachother at all. I dont read either of your journals because im afraid of what they might say. i dont want to read about us not being close anymore or about you hating me so i just choose to not know whats going on. its just strange that we are both online and not talkin to eachother, that i have your dress but dont know when ill see you to give it back to you when 3 months ago the answer would be that u would already have your dress and i wouldnt be talking to you online because you would be here doing something random with me. i can accept that things change i just want you to know that i didnt ever ever want to hurt you. i know that i went about things wrong and didnt really help anything and im sorry and i understand that you cant forget that.

thank yous are in order for my lovely friends who had to recently take care of a drunk mess of an ami two nights in a row. thank you guys so much for being there while i was crying like and idiot and puking like a belemic. i love you guys for it... and karma will repay u! and special thanks to the guest hero of the nite who will never read this... thank u for getting me so fucked up and not asking me to buy u beer and taking care of me when i was sick and not taking advantage of the situation... u are truly an awsome guy... sorry u got stranded

im going on a college visit in 3 hours and i cant sleep because i hate that you left me. you were my stability. ive been trying to fill the void wtih hair dye, tattoos,antidepressants, alcohol, drugs, meaningless nights with meaningless boys, but when im alone at 230 in the morning turns out none of it worked. i hate that i was so easy for u to leave and i hate that your happy and i hate that you have katie and i hate that you dont miss me at all and i hate that i cant see you with out wanting to cry and i hate that when i do see you i cant touch you and i hate that i dont know when the last time we kissed was and i hate that im alone crying at 230 in the morning when 3 months ago i would be asleep with you right now i hate that im hurting like this and i hate that you did it to me but in reality i did it to myself and more than anything else i hate that i still need you... i just never thought ud be the one to leave

So, is that what you call a getaway?
Tell me what you got away with.
Cause I've seen more spine in jellyfish.
I've seen more guts in eleven-year-old kids.

... possibly the one ur dating...
Have another drink and drive yourself home.
.... o wait i forgot uve already done that one...
I hope there's ice on all the roads.
And you can think of me when you forget your seatbelt,
and again when your head goes through the windshield.

i was thinking today and that trailer totally defined my summer and changed my life... funny how things work out. a couple of weeks there full of underwear, alcohol, and cigarettes flipped my life upside down. it formed strong friendships, gave me the label "annorexic (sp?) crack whore, ruined relationships, stripped me of my remaining innocence, allowed me to meet a real live rock star, and taught us all a lesson in "slumming it." the funny part is that the owner of this trailer has no clue being that he was gone in europe for all of this. it wasnt one significant event that happened... im not really even sure what it was, only that pretty much everything is different now, im still the same person just living with very different circumstances. even tho it was mostly bad... i wouldnt take ne of it back. heres to the trailer

i didnt realize it would be this hard. i didnt realize i would miss him so much. and missing him makes me wonder if its because i want to be with him or just because hes all i know. it makes me wonder if i should just give in and go back. but if i do that ill regret it... i have to at least try this whole on my own thing even if its only for a couple weeks... so far ive only lasted 2 days. its so hard... hes hurting so much and he doesnt see that i am too. mikes there to temporarily dull the pain but in the end it just makes it that much harder.
sometimes you just need a long drive with the tom petty blasting, a good confession, and a couple of chili dogs... feeling much better. i realized i dont know what im doing but thats ok

i had a good day... erika al and i took a road trip to Pitt (only ours was DUI free) then i went to dinner with vanessa and then we saw her puppy and then i watched the breakfast club with al and erika bc i was left out of the loop and invite for other plans. we didnt find that much we liked but it was still fun. i somehow jsut figured out kat is taking abby to the beach... i feel strange about it... not mad and just suprised but i cant be upset i wouldnt have gone neway cuz im flaky like that

i dont want al to leave so much :(

and i dont want soccer to start for erika

and i dont want robby to come home... its so much easier to jsut not deal with

and i wish i could take beautiful pictures of myself like rachyl... i dont even have to take them myself someone else could take them... ive never liked the way i looked in a single picture

and i wish i could find sunglasses that didnt make me look like an ass

and i wish i knew a better way to deal with all of this

and i wish i could explain why or understand why i did what i did

and i wish the text message i just got was from someone else who i wish was thinking about me but i kno is not

and i wish i didnt wish that

and i wish i knew what was the right decision

and i wish i knew that i didnt still need him

and i wish i could still be madly in love with him

and i wish that our unit could stay this close forever

and i wish i could make myself do something productive this summer

and i wish i could make myself care nemore about nething... but i cant

and i wish that if i left my friends would care so much that theyd make me a good bye video like als ... but they wouldnt

most of all... i wish i knew what i was running from

i dont regret nething ive done

wat if im digging my own grave

but theres no where left to go
no one left to run to
